SerialPort for Erlang

This is a simple implementation pf a serialport erlang-port, which works on
Linux and Windows.

Exanples:
SP = serial:start().
SP ! { enumerate }.


SP = serial:start([ { enumerate } ]).


SP = serial:start([ { baudrate, 19200 }, { open, "/dev/ttyUSB1" } ]).
SP ! { send, "hello" }.
SP ! { close }.
SP ! stop.
